        <h2
          class="text-5xl text-center font-semibold tracking-tight text-white sm:text-7xl lg:text-left"
        >
          Emprendimiento, Inteligencia y Ciencia
        </h2>
        <p
          class="mt-8 text-center text-pretty text-lg font-medium text-gray-300 sm:text-xl/8 lg:text-left"
        >
          En CEIDI, brindamos una educación integral y de excelencia, para
          potenciar el crecimiento intelectual y emocional de cada estudiante.
        </p>
      </div>
      <div class="mx-auto mt-10 max-w-2xl lg:mx-0 lg:max-w-none">
        <div
          class="grid grid-cols-1 gap-x-8 gap-y-6 text-base/7 font-semibold text-white sm:grid-cols-2 md:flex lg:gap-x-10"
        >
          <!-- <a href="#">Open roles <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
              <a href="#">Internship program <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
              <a href="#">Our values <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a>
              <a href="#">Meet our leadership <span aria-hidden="true">&rarr;</span></a> -->
        </div>
        <dl class="mt-16 flex gap-8 sm:mt-20 justify-center lg:justify-start">
          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse gap-1">
            <dt class="text-base/7 text-gray-300">Niños en Preescolar</dt>
            <dd class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">7+</dd>
          </div>
          <div class="flex flex-col-reverse gap-1">
            <dt class="text-base/7 text-gray-300">Básica Primaria</dt>
            <dd class="text-4xl font-semibold tracking-tight text-white">7+</dd>
          </div>
        </dl>
      </div>
    </div>
    <button
      class="bg-green-700 shadow-lg shadow-green-700/50 text-white font-bold self-center py-3 w-[80vw] rounded-xl mt-12 lg:w-[30vw]"
